OL,3,CAnger as Bristol Rovers refers to
OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,F"I'm a disabled man. Just because I no
OL,7,Flonger use a wheelchair doesn't mean
OL,8,FI'm not," he posted on social media.
OL,10,F"Disabled people are normal people.
OL,11,FJust because I'm disabled doesn't make
OL,12,Fme any less normal than anyone else.
OL,13,FWording is so key sometimes. Do
OL,14,Fbetter."
OL,16,FJake later posted a video message and
OL,17,Fsaid: "I can get very tired and
OL,18,Fsometimes it is difficult for me to
OL,19,Fget around.
