OL,3,CAnger as Bristol Rovers refers to
OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,FOn Tuesday 7 May, the Supporters' Club
OL,7,Ftook down their original post sharing
OL,8,Fthe letter.
OL,10,FIn a statement the club said: "Bristol
OL,11,FRovers Football Club would like to
OL,12,Fapologise for any offence caused by an
OL,13,Ferror in wording in a recent
OL,14,Fcommunication regarding disabled
OL,15,Fsupporters.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
