OL,3,CAnger as Bristol Rovers refers to
OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,F"No harmful intention of meaning was
OL,7,Fever intended in the wording, which
OL,8,Fwas included in a private email
OL,9,Fexchange between the Club and a
OL,10,Frepresentative from the Bristol Rovers
OL,11,FSupporters Club.
OL,13,F"The Club is proud of our ongoing
OL,14,Fcommitment to provide the best
OL,15,Fexperience for all supporters of
OL,16,FBristol Rovers FC, in particular our
OL,17,Fwork with the Club's Disabled
OL,18,FSupporters Association to ensure fans
OL,19,Fwith accessibility or additional needs
OL,20,Fare able to enjoy each and every match
OL,21,Fat The Memorial Stadium.
